PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1995-919 which corrects the status of the appointment of PATRICIA C. COURSEY, a Governor of the Canadian Centre for Occupational Health and Safety, who should have been appointed as "being the nominee of the Lieutenant Governor in Council of Ontario" instead of as "a representative of Employer Organizations".
